28:46.058 --> 28:49.660
And hope that they can
stay up late enough
to see their mother.

28:50.161 --> 28:51.328
I know the hours
you're keeping.

28:51.330 --> 28:54.431
I know that you're working
around the clock.

28:54.433 --> 28:56.066
But there's no
good argument that says

28:56.068 --> 28:57.301
Waiting for their mother
to get home from work

28:57.303 --> 29:00.370
Is better for them
than being with their father
for six weeks

29:00.372 --> 29:04.007
And letting him show them
a little piece of the world.

29:12.183 --> 29:14.284
Flo: Who's there?

29:15.754 --> 29:16.487
It's me, austin.

29:16.489 --> 29:19.123
You're not the man
from across the street,
are you?

29:19.125 --> 29:21.091
The one I've seen
watching me

29:21.093 --> 29:23.060
Through the curtains?

29:23.062 --> 29:25.062
Yes, that's me.

29:25.530 --> 29:30.067
I can see
into your bathroom.
Not the bathroom.

29:30.069 --> 29:31.368
The bedroom.

29:31.370 --> 29:34.138
I can see
into your bedroom.

29:34.205 --> 29:36.340
(footsteps pattering)

29:36.407 --> 29:39.176
Promise me you're not
going to hurt me.

29:39.178 --> 29:41.779
Of course
I'm not gonna...

29:44.549 --> 29:45.682
Grab me by the hair.

29:45.684 --> 29:47.851
Really?
Mmm-hmm.

29:47.919 --> 29:49.787
Like this?
Harder.

29:49.789 --> 29:51.288
You sure?
Mmm-hmm.

29:51.290 --> 29:52.523
Drag me up the stairs.

29:52.525 --> 29:53.857
Drag you
up the stairs?

29:53.859 --> 29:54.758
If you do, I'll scream.

29:54.760 --> 29:57.227
Someone'll hear you
and they'll call the police,

29:57.229 --> 30:00.230
And they'll take
you away to jail.

30:01.132 --> 30:03.734
Any time you want
to jump in here.

30:03.736 --> 30:05.702
Uh, but I'll be
acquitted.

30:05.970 --> 30:09.206
When the jury sees you,
they'll understand

30:09.208 --> 30:11.842
Why I couldn't
control myself.

30:11.844 --> 30:14.211
Well, I'm not gonna
let you take me upstairs.

30:14.213 --> 30:16.613
Okay, so you want
to do it here?

30:16.615 --> 30:18.916
Even though I know
you want me in that bed,

30:18.918 --> 30:21.919
The bed you've watched me
make love in.

30:21.921 --> 30:23.153
So wait, we do go upstairs?

30:23.155 --> 30:25.289
Not if I have
any say in it.

30:25.657 --> 30:27.324
I'm confused.

30:27.458 --> 30:30.460
I'm going upstairs,
locking the door
behind me

30:30.462 --> 30:31.762
And calling the police.

30:31.764 --> 30:33.030
You just try
to kick it down.

30:33.032 --> 30:36.300
Even if you get in,
I'll never give in to you.

30:46.945 --> 30:48.946
Are you coming?

30:54.919 --> 30:58.088
Oh! Bill and virginia,
bernadette and kyle.

30:58.090 --> 31:00.424
Bernadette and kyle,
bill and virginia.

31:00.426 --> 31:01.725
Hello, nice to meet you.

31:01.727 --> 31:02.426
It's dr. Masters.

31:02.428 --> 31:04.795
I'm not sure exactly
how this is going to work.

31:04.797 --> 31:08.265
Oh, well, dwight says
that your cameraman
didn't get footage

31:08.267 --> 31:10.601
Of you conducting
any intake interviews.

31:10.603 --> 31:12.336
So we're gonna
have them sit in,

31:12.338 --> 31:15.205
As if they're a couple
coming to you for help.

31:15.207 --> 31:16.139
Help with what?

31:16.141 --> 31:17.941
Roger:
With their sex life.

31:17.943 --> 31:20.110
We don't help couples
have sex,

31:20.112 --> 31:22.246
We observe them
having sex.

31:22.248 --> 31:22.946
In that whole process,

31:22.948 --> 31:25.048
That's definitely gonna
be part of the story,
certainly.

31:25.050 --> 31:28.752
Um, but I think
the centerpiece
is the work you're doing

31:28.754 --> 31:30.754
That goes beyond
educating the public

31:30.756 --> 31:31.488
As to how the body works

31:31.490 --> 31:34.858
And puts that knowledge
to practical use
with treatment.

31:34.860 --> 31:35.626
We talked about this.

31:35.628 --> 31:37.828
We haven't gotten
to treating dysfunction.

31:37.830 --> 31:40.130
We're still in
the very early stages
of that.

31:40.132 --> 31:44.101
All we really need is
a few shots of you two
taking to a couple.

31:44.103 --> 31:47.304
And over that
we're gonna hear
something like,

31:47.306 --> 31:50.374
"masters and
johnson's study

31:50.376 --> 31:52.242
"is poised to break
new ground

31:52.244 --> 31:54.578
"in the treatment
of sexual dysfunction."

31:54.580 --> 31:55.212
And you are poised,

31:55.214 --> 31:58.048
So we're not saying
anything that isn't true.
Exactly.

31:58.050 --> 32:02.753
Roger: This will amount to
no more than 15 seconds
of screen time.

32:02.755 --> 32:03.420
It's just a visual.

32:03.422 --> 32:08.725
Frankly, we can't use
the footage you already have,
it's just...

32:08.727 --> 32:09.927
It's too graphic.

32:09.929 --> 32:11.261
I'd never allow it
anyway.

32:11.263 --> 32:12.396
The understanding
with patients

32:12.398 --> 32:14.865
Is that footage
is confidential,

32:14.867 --> 32:16.500
For research
purposes only,

32:16.502 --> 32:17.434
Not as a calling card

32:17.436 --> 32:19.403
For services
we don't provide.

32:19.405 --> 32:21.471
Roger: That's the case
for working with a couple

32:21.473 --> 32:24.241
Whose privacy
you're not
actually violating,

32:24.243 --> 32:27.277
Who've actually signed up
to be filmed.

32:27.745 --> 32:29.880
And are you a couple?

32:29.882 --> 32:31.682
We met just now
in the lobby.

32:31.684 --> 32:34.084
Turns out, we went
to the same high school.

32:34.086 --> 32:35.118
So you've hired actors?

32:35.120 --> 32:36.086
Virginia:
Will you excuse me?

32:36.088 --> 32:38.488
Where are you going?
Just for a moment.

32:38.490 --> 32:40.190
Virginia.

32:40.658 --> 32:42.960
Bill, what is
the problem here?

32:42.962 --> 32:46.330
If your own patients
won't participate...

32:46.332 --> 32:47.397
But they're led to believe

32:47.399 --> 32:49.566
I exploit other patients
for my own purposes?

32:49.568 --> 32:52.703
Really? You don't see that
as a problem?

32:52.904 --> 32:54.237
Well...

32:54.239 --> 32:56.039
You've never
been to court?

32:56.041 --> 32:59.509
Had any reason
to modify his visitation?
No.

32:59.511 --> 33:03.480
And he's been responsible
while they've been
in his custody?

33:03.482 --> 33:05.782
For the most part.

33:06.384 --> 33:06.783
(sighs)

33:06.785 --> 33:10.187
Yes, he has
been responsible.

33:10.189 --> 33:12.322
Any reason to think
that might change?

33:12.324 --> 33:17.260
That they wouldn't
be safe with him
or with the new wife?

33:17.262 --> 33:17.861
No.

33:17.863 --> 33:20.697
You offering them
something better?

33:20.898 --> 33:23.367
Well, we always spend
the holidays together.

33:23.369 --> 33:25.569
We have a lot
of christmas traditions.

33:25.571 --> 33:28.338
They would be
missing all of that.

33:28.406 --> 33:33.243
So they swap one christmas
for six weeks in europe?

33:34.245 --> 33:37.748
I think they'd
come out ahead,
don't you?

33:38.416 --> 33:41.651
And would it be
such an awful thing
for you?

33:41.653 --> 33:44.755
I see the way you
run around here,
the hours you keep.

33:44.757 --> 33:48.658
The second you're through,
the way you bolt
for the elevator,

33:48.660 --> 33:50.527
Probably racing
straight home

33:50.529 --> 33:52.829
For tuck-in time,
am I right?

33:52.831 --> 33:55.866
Of course I'm right.
You're a mother.

33:55.868 --> 33:56.700
I know mothers.

33:56.702 --> 34:00.670
Most of them could
use a little break
every now and then.

34:00.672 --> 34:03.273
Maybe one way
to look at this is that

34:03.275 --> 34:06.843
Your ex is offering you
a little vacation, too.

34:06.845 --> 34:09.880
Uh, I... I don't
want a vacation

34:09.882 --> 34:12.349
From my children,
mr. Spleeb.

34:12.351 --> 34:15.318
Look, you could say no.

34:15.420 --> 34:16.620
I could?
Yeah.

34:16.622 --> 34:18.855
Technically,
you have the right.

34:18.857 --> 34:22.159
But I would
caution you against it.

34:22.161 --> 34:25.996
Why give him reason
to revisit, uh,
a custody arrangement,

34:25.998 --> 34:29.366
Which, on the whole,
is working for both of you?

34:29.368 --> 34:34.504
