organized by the sclc.

38:09.788 --> 38:11.421
Oh.

38:13.224 --> 38:16.359
You know what
the sclc is, right?

38:16.661 --> 38:18.495
Of course, the...

38:18.596 --> 38:20.897
The south
carolina liberation...

38:20.899 --> 38:24.834
