the specifics, yes.

39:19.257 --> 39:24.994
But I understand
what the fight is about,
and I believe in it.

39:25.229 --> 39:26.796
Why?

39:26.798 --> 39:29.065
I want to hear
your reasons.

39:29.067 --> 39:31.368
Another test.

39:31.370 --> 39:32.635
You know what I think?

39:32.637 --> 39:36.439
