people assume.

41:40.332 --> 41:41.130
We explained that.

41:41.132 --> 41:45.034
Honestly, I don't think
people assume it.

41:45.036 --> 41:46.870
No offense.

41:46.872 --> 41:49.939
But a girl like that,
a guy like you...

41:49.941 --> 41:51.441
Excuse me?

41:51.443 --> 41:52.609
I know how it is.

41:52.611 --> 41:54.544
My maxine is a real dish.

41:54.546 --> 41:56.479
I get "the beauty
and the beast" constantly.

41:56.481 --> 41:58.047
Roger: Okay, everyone,
break's over.

41:58.049 --> 42:00.717
Back in the conference room
in 10.

42:01.819 --> 42:03.686
Make sure jeremy
powders you up.

42:03.688 --> 42:06.155
You got a real shine
going there.

42:07.892 --> 42:11.027
I know bill keeps a box
of extra shirt buttons
in here somewhere.

42:11.029 --> 42:14.230
Robert:
What do you reckon
that babysitter thought?

42:14.232 --> 42:17.267
You bringing a negro man
into your house?

42:17.701 --> 42:19.068
Well, she's not...

42:19.070 --> 42:21.504
She's a neighbor,
just helping out
for today.

42:21.506 --> 42:24.574
You heard
what I told her.
We work together.

42:24.576 --> 42:27.076
A negro man
in a torn shirt?

42:27.078 --> 42:29.245
Elaine is not a gossip.

42:30.614 --> 42:34.017
Her daughter sissy
married a mexican man.

42:35.219 --> 42:39.088
Here, we go.
Shirt, please.

42:40.157 --> 42:42.025
It'll make this easier.

42:42.027 --> 42:43.293
No, ma'am.

42:43.295 --> 42:46.696
Fine, I will sew
with you in it.

42:46.698 --> 42:49.399
Go sit by the light.

42:50.301 --> 42:53.736
Not in this room.
Not there.

42:53.738 --> 42:56.205
Virginia: Now, doesn't
that sound exciting?

42:56.207 --> 42:58.608
We miss school
on top of it?

42:58.610 --> 42:59.275
No spinning, henry.

42:59.277 --> 43:01.811
Yes, we'll have to
check with ms. Braddock
and mrs. Alexander,

43:01.813 --> 43:05.748
And you have to promise
