43:12.691 --> 43:15.792
This is a special treat,
dinner here with your mom,

43:15.794 --> 43:16.859
So you behave, okay?

43:16.861 --> 43:20.463
Pam, do you mind
giving us a few minutes?

43:20.465 --> 43:21.931
Oh, sure, no problem.

43:21.933 --> 43:23.967
What if I find
some crispy green beans?

43:23.969 --> 43:25.969
No almond cookies
for you, tessy,

43:25.971 --> 43:27.403
Until you eat your greens.

43:27.405 --> 43:29.339
